27904" style="width: 480px; height: 640px;" /></p></div><!-- /.ss-content-block --><div class="ss-content-block col-2-3"><h2><span class="green-text"><span class="red-text">Welcome Present & Future Customers!</span></span></h2><p>Greetings. My name is Richard Bramen, owner of America’s Favorite Flags. I’m a proud Veteran that volunteered and served on-board our U.S. Navy Submarines, active and inactive for 30 years. So, to me, when I see “The Red, White, and Blue” waving, it represents the people that devote themselves to the service of our country. I truly enjoy selling American Flags because they remind me of those who fought for our country in the past as well as the brave men and women still fighting for us today. Yes, each one of us serves our country in different ways, but, “Old Glory” represents our Country’s ongoing belief in freedom and in one another. <strong>HONOR ALL WHO SERVE: Proudly Fly Your American Flag!</strong></p><p><a class="small-action-button" href="/richard-s-history">More of Richard's Story</a></p></div><!-- /.ss-content-block --></div></div><!-- /.ss-section-wrap --><div class="ss-section-wrap equal-heights"><div class="ss-section-wrap-inner"><div class="ss-content-block col-2 hp-extra-padding-top-bottom"><h2><span class="green-text">Free Features with Each American Flag Purchased:</span></h2><ul><li><big><strong>FREE REINFORCED FLY END HEMS</strong></big></li><li><big><strong>FREE SHIPPING in the Continental United States</strong></big></li><li><big><strong>NO TAXES—Except in Missouri</strong></big></li></ul><h2><span class="green-text">Simple to Order</span></h2><p>Choose from 2 fabrics, select your 100% American-Made, U.S.A. Flag size, then put in how many flags you want, and check out. Boom! Your flag is on the way.</p><h2 style="color:#c0392b;">Save With Our <strong>BUY-2-FLAGS SPECIAL OFFER!</strong></h2><p><a class="small-action-button" href="/shop-usa-flags">Price Charts</a></p></div><!-- /.ss-content-block --><div class="ss-content